Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了一台新的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有人會還沒確定對方是否有威脅就背對著他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在快逃吧  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更在意那幾個小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯·斯圖爾特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1218,969)\fs54}loader
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊確認到先行派出的多腳裝載機機能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及代號利瑪的目標正在移動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瑪正在移動？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  就得要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算開溜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是量產機  但這也是能力過硬的軍用規格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巖盤要塌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是為重逢高興的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了  多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉  拜託我拿的麵包…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐時間什麼的早就過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方的資料在數據庫中也沒有符合的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯示利瑪反應的少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉  修特·普萊斯中校請您立刻前往本廳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,969)\fs54}Giftdium
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從天賜礦石裏出現的女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真有這種不可思議的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦  要送她去管理局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等她醒來再決定也不遲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  軍隊牽扯在裏面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能隨便把這事公開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  一臉苦思的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃點甜食  慢慢考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1239,969)\fs54}Tarte Tatin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話  嘗嘗我的法式蘋果撻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法式蘋果撻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說她是在模仿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼  能不能調查一下她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要查  不清楚身份的情況下也沒法查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等她能把情況都告訴我們的時候  再做詳細調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙  到那時為止能先把這孩子寄放在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  不是和宗吾住在一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要住下  佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼宗吾  羅曼所說的話不聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個少女的事告一段落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚的事情暫且擱置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我說服你父母之前  你先別去見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那樣事情會變得麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧  多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  把飢渴的雜犬和嬌小可愛的少女放在一起可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是雜犬也不飢渴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老犬也有一隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺腳下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就借浴室一用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是多蒙的醃菜石？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把這種和醃菜石混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是塊罕見的石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的軍隊  對您來說很不喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去  大尉在大戰時代所立的功勳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是年輕時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯·斯圖爾特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在芬克魯夫秘密開發完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八世代強襲格鬥專用BPA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個再棒不過的玩具了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會接受的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你的能力有著很高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1137,969)\fs54}Efreet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,設計代號名  伊夫利特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話一定能十二分發揮出這台機體的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以  不過部下要由我來選拔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮好柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睫毛也好長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮膚也好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  將已經氧化的膜削掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了自由就是我說了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能保護菲莉雅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你們帶回來的那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼無法變身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是的  這樣亂動怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼紋章會在你的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點  要是太吵的話會被大家發現的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好吹乾頭髮會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是不習慣吹風機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿莉控？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  我不是蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別用你的髒手亂碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這裏警戒很嚴密  但也不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你有什麼奇怪舉動  不管理由我們都會開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂開槍  會傷到同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來歸隊的測試沒必要了呢  帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍傷沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈已經取出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口的出血  通過緊繃肌肉能夠止住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧  這可是我的特技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚想必也會湛藍無比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等母親般的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星吉夫特將開始邁向真正的繁榮與安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時機現已成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如您所言  佐恩·波伊魯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我是佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  你是菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  收音機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於菲莉雅來說當然會開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候過來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為都是些第一次見到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是人們的歡笑還是傳遞來的感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是季節於風中所散發出的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦或是令人陶醉的夕陽所帶來的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  咖喱做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我拿到桌上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  能把這個拿給宗吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手  不能隨便使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.87,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}胸に溢れる音が言葉に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.87,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}內心所涌現出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.73,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}なりそうでならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.73,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無法很好地表達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:17.89,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}見つめるだけだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:17.89,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只是靜靜地看著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:22.51,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それでもココロ繋がるような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:22.51,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便如此仍感覺我們心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:25.84,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}いつも　近くにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:25.84,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論何時  都想依偎在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:33.25,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}手を伸ばして触れるだけでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:33.25,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便只是伸手輕撫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:36.11,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:36.11,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也會無比高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:44.24,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どこからくるのこの気持ち　わからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:44.24,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這份感受究竟從何而來  不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:52.71,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}教えて　空はどうしてこんな広いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:52.71,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}告訴我  天空為何這般廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:22:56.36,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}広すぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:22:56.36,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如此地寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:59.73,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほっぼり出したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:59.73,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好想展翅翱翔其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:03.99,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今にときめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:03.99,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如今的這份悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.82,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}吸い込まれそうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.82,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}彷彿被深深吸引一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:19.60,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}強く　強く　掴まえて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:19.60,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要緊緊  牢牢  將其抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從大地來到藍天之下的菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身處這自由的風中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋狂的陷阱不斷逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「彗星·路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,靛藍花園
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起將這冒險之票握入手中吧
